Sheik Dahiru Bauchi, supreme leader of the Islamic Sufi group known as the Tijaniyyah, has endorsed the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) Presidential Candidate, Atiku Abubakar, for the 2023 elections. The prominent Islamic scholar endorsed Atiku in a message to his followers. “You can’t bite true believer twice, some people were saying vote for who will continue from where they stop, we didn’t enjoy where they stopped. “Majority of my People told me that they will vote for Atiku , and I will not leave my people, I will be with my people  to see what almighty Allah will do. “We are praying to Allah to give Nigeria the best leader who will ease the sufferings of Nigeria and bring rapid development.” Chairman, Sheikh Dahiru Usman Bauchi Foundation, Ibrahim Dahiru Bauchi, confirmed to Daily Trust that the audio where the Sheikh spoke is real.